  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15109">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 1. </span>
      Explain the proper safety procedures to follow when preparing surfaces and
      applying coatings. <br /><i>Resource:</i>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vpr3e_erug" target="_blank"
        >Interior Painting Safety (video)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15104">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 2. </span>
      Do the following:
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-15104 mb-requirement-id-15105">
        (a) Explain three ways that coatings can improve a surface. <br /><i
          >Resource:</i
        >
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A-ERekKoohI" target="_blank"
          >Epoxy Resin Coatings (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-15104 mb-requirement-id-15106">
        (b) Explain the differences between oil-based paints, acrylic-based
        paints, and water-based paints. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jEyTpUfbrYA" target="_blank"
          >Paints - Oil, Water, Enamel, Acrylic (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T99OFHCLF4s" target="_blank"
          >Water vs Oil Based Paints (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-15104 mb-requirement-id-15107">
        (c) Explain where you would apply enamel paint, flat paint, wood stain,
        and varnish, and explain the importance of sheen. <br /><i>Resource:</i>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DyKh80Yt9k0" target="_blank"
          >Paint Sheen Differences Explained (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-15104 mb-requirement-id-15108">
        (d) Tell why each is best for these uses.
      </li>
    </ul>
    <div style="padding-left: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: #515354"></div>
    <br />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15110">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 3. </span>
      Prepare and paint two different surfaces using patching materials or
      caulking and the proper primers and topcoats. Suggested projects include
      an interior or exterior wall, a door, a piece of furniture, a concrete
      wall or floor, a porch rail, or a fence. Your counselor must preapprove
      the projects. <br /><i>Resource:</i>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CRXCB_3gLok" target="_blank"
        >How to Paint a Room (video)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15111">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 4. </span>
      Prepare and paint an item using harmonizing colors that you have selected
      using the color wheel in the <em>Painting</em> merit badge pamphlet.
      <br /><i>Resources:</i>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K75ynD7aAeg" target="_blank"
        >Choosing a Color Palette for Your Home (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a
        href="https://filestore.scouting.org/filestore/Merit_Badge_ReqandRes/Requirement%20Resources/Painting/Painting_Color%20Wheet%20from%202025%20MBP.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        >Color Wheel from Painting Merit Badge Pamphlet (PDF)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15112">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 5. </span>
      Show the right way to use, clean, maintain, and store painting equipment.
      <br /><i>Resources:</i>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C_bY5_mOTcY" target="_blank"
        >Good Paint Hygiene (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=u6_e5YXgviY" target="_blank"
        >How to Clean and Store Paint Brushes (video)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15113">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 6. </span>
      Explain the importance of ladder safety, personal hygiene, and the use of
      personal protective equipment when painting. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b7ArZilnnTE" target="_blank"
        >Ladder Safety (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=67G06bhuxPA" target="_blank"
        >Personal Protective Equipment for Painting (PPE) (video)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15114">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 7. </span>
      Explain some of the environmental and health issues concerning removing
      paint, applying paint, and discarding old paint. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7YKuwlGgWpc" target="_blank"
        >How to Dispose of Old Paint (video)</a
      ><br />
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8lG6dAZE52k" target="_blank"
        >Paint Removers (video)</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mb-requirement-item">
    <div class="mb-requirement-parent mb-requirement-id-15115">
      <span class="mb-requirement-listnumber"> 8. </span>
      Do ONE of the following:
    </div>
    <ul class="mb-requirement-children-list">
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-15115 mb-requirement-id-15116">
        (a) Explore careers related to this merit badge. Research one career to
        learn about the training and education needed, costs, job prospects,
        salary, job duties, and career advancement. Your research methods may
        include—with your parent or guardian's permission—an internet or library
        search, an interview with a professional in the field, or a visit to a
        location where people in this career work. Discuss with your counselor
        both your findings and what about this profession might make it an
        interesting career. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/5glRwgnb5gk" target="_blank"
          >Painters Career Overview (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a href="https://youtu.be/mWjbRoAId_4" target="_blank"
          >Scenic Painter (video)</a
        >
      </li>
      <li class="mb-requirement-child mb-parent-15115 mb-requirement-id-15117">
        (b) Explore how you could use knowledge and skills from this merit badge
        to pursue a hobby or healthy lifestyle. Research any training needed,
        expenses, and organizations that promote or support it. Discuss with
        your counselor what short-term and long-term goals you might have if you
        pursued this. <br /><i>Resources:</i>
        <a href="https://youtu.be/L4ADLL2gAtU" target="_blank"
          >How to Paint Murals Like a Pro (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a
          href="https://youtu.be/UpImD3qedKw?si=CotiHOXpynF-JptZ"
          target="_blank"
          >Easy Wall Painting DIY I Balcony Makeover I Yoga Wall Art (video)</a
        ><br />
        <a
          href="https://www.marthastewart.com/8229238/mood-boosting-paint-colors"
          target="_blank"
          >Mood-Boosting Paint Colors for Every Room in Your House (website)</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
